graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamGetUsers (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamFindUser (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	iamFindUserById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:IamUpdateUserInput!)
{
	iamUpdateUser (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	iamDeleteUserById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamDeleteUsers (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		password
		isTwoFactorAuthenticationEnabled
		twoFactorAuthenticationSecret
		rememberToken
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
